COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 1:54PM PT today, over 1.3 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 24.9 thousand have died.

In the last day, 3 thousand new infections were reported and 11 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 18.4 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 51% have their 1st shot and 4.2% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 2 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~8 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-04 and fully vaccinated by Aug-15. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
